name: AUDIO_CODEC_PROFILE_TYPE
description:
The codec type of the output audio stream for CDN live
            streaming. The default value is LC-ACC.

parameters.AUDIO_CODEC_PROFILE_LC_AAC: 0: (Default) LC-AAC, which is the low-complexity audio codec type.

parameters.AUDIO_CODEC_PROFILE_HE_AAC: 1: HE-AAC, which is the high-efficiency audio codec type.
